The paper is about texture synthesis using convolutional neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for texture synthesis also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the deep representations learned by convolutional neural networks, which falls under neural networks (cs.NE) and graphics (cs.GR).
